cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR 

This paper deals with scene-text understanding and text extraction from images, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the incorporation of Rotation Region Proposal Networks (RRPN) in the text extraction pipeline, which is a deep learning technique and hence falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the paper discusses the practical deployment of the model, which involves information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques.
